Aeroflot Proposes Move to Rubles From Euro, Interfax Reports

-- B y   S c o t t   R o s e
-- 
2011-07-27T16:30:21Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-27/aeroflot-proposes-move-to-rubles-from-euro-interfax-reports.html
OAO Aeroflot,  Russia ’s largest
airline, has proposed that the country’s carriers stop linking
their fares to the euro and switch to the ruble, Interfax
reported, citing an unidentified person at the airline.  To contact the reporter on this story:
